statements: SELECT * FROM program_impact WHERE program_id = 1;
SELECT program_name, impact_description FROM program_impact WHERE awareness_level > 3;
SELECT program_id, program_name, advocacy_level FROM program_impact WHERE impact_type = 'Education';
SELECT program_name, impact_description, awareness_level FROM program_impact WHERE advocacy_level < 2;
SELECT program_name, advocacy_level FROM program_impact WHERE impact_description LIKE '%community%';
SELECT * FROM program_impact WHERE impact_type = 'Social' ORDER BY awareness_level DESC, advocacy_level ASC
SELECT program_id, program_name, impact_type FROM program_impact WHERE advocacy_level > 5 ORDER BY program_name
SELECT program_name, impact_description FROM program_impact WHERE awareness_level < 3 AND advocacy_level > 5
SELECT impact_description FROM program_impact WHERE impact_type = 'Environmental'
SELECT program_id, program_name, awareness_level FROM program_impact ORDER BY awareness_level DESC
SELECT * FROM program_impact;
SELECT program_name, awareness_score FROM program_impact ORDER BY awareness_score DESC;
SELECT program_id, program_name, awareness_score, advocacy_score FROM program_impact WHERE awareness_score > 50;
SELECT * FROM participant_details JOIN program_impact ON participant_details.program_id = program_impact.program_id;
SELECT participant_name, program_name FROM program_impact JOIN participant_details ON program_impact.program_id = participant_details.program_id ORDER BY program_name ASC;
SELECT * FROM program_impact WHERE awareness_score > 50 ORDER BY program_name ASC;
SELECT program_name, awareness_score, advocacy_score FROM program_impact WHERE advocacy_score > 30;
SELECT program_name, advocacy_score FROM program_impact WHERE awareness_score < 40 ORDER BY advocacy_score DESC;
SELECT * FROM participant_details pd JOIN program_impact pi ON pd.program_id = pi.program_id WHERE pd.participant_name LIKE '%John%' AND pi.awareness_score > 60;
SELECT pd.participant_name, pi.program_name FROM participant_details pd JOIN program_impact pi ON pd.program_id = pi.program_id WHERE pi.advocacy_score < 50;
SELECT * FROM Program;
SELECT program_name, program_description FROM Program ORDER BY program_name ASC;
SELECT * FROM Participant WHERE start_date >= '2022-01-01' AND start_date <= '2022-12-31';
SELECT impact_score, impact_date FROM Impact ORDER BY impact_score DESC, impact_date ASC;
SELECT p.first_name, p.last_name, i.impact_score FROM Participant p JOIN Impact i ON p.participant_id = i.participant_id WHERE i.impact_score >= 80;
SELECT * FROM Program WHERE program_id = 1;
SELECT program_name, program_start_date FROM Program ORDER BY program_start_date DESC;
SELECT * FROM Participant WHERE start_date BETWEEN '2022-01-01' AND '2022-12-31';
SELECT program_name, impact_score FROM Program INNER JOIN Impact ON Program.program_id = Impact.program_id WHERE Impact.impact_score >= 80;

SELECT p.first_name, p.last_name, COUNT(i.impact_id) AS num_impacts FROM Participant p LEFT JOIN Impact i ON p.participant_id = i.participant_id GROUP BY p.participant_id HAVING num_impacts >= 3 ORDER BY num_impacts DESC;

SELECT e.evaluator_name, e.evaluation_score, p.program_name FROM program_evaluation e INNER JOIN impact_of_educational_programs p ON e.program_id = p.id WHERE e.evaluation_score > 80
